# Mini App UI Rules

## Design system doc

Canonical reference: [DESIGN_SYSTEM.md](../../DESIGN_SYSTEM.md) (v1.8.5 shell + v1.9/v2.0 addenda). Token source: [apps/mini-app/src/style.css](../../apps/mini-app/src/style.css).

## v1.6 UI patterns

- **Milestone chip** (HUD) ‚Äî `Manager in X.y` / `CEO in X.y` progress during play
- **Death cause row** (game over) ‚Äî icon + label per failure type
- **Retry tip** (game over) ‚Äî satirical one-liner from `constants.ts`
- **Tap-zone glow** ‚Äî `tap-zone-left/right:active` border feedback
- Co-branding: [`lib/branding.ts`](../../apps/mini-app/src/lib/branding.ts), `VITE_PROMPT_ANATOMY_URL` (optional env)

## v1.8.2 UI patterns (F&F bundle)

- **Tap deck** ‚Äî `#tapControlsBar` with visible TAP LEFT / TAP RIGHT (snippet-style)
- **HUD tap hint** ‚Äî `#hudTapHint` + `.tap-deck-hint` pulse for first 5 taps
- **HR memo rail** ‚Äî in-run announcements below game HUD; `showHrMemoCombined()` for multi-line memos
- **Responsive ladder** ‚Äî `#ladderTrack` fills shared content column at 320px / 390px
- **Home** ‚Äî scroll on short Telegram viewports; amber news strip + shift description
- **Viewport QA** ‚Äî `npm run qa:viewport` after layout changes (50% play-area ratio; tap deck outside `#gamePlayArea`)

## v1.8.3+ layout column

- **`#gameContentColumn`** ‚Äî single `cl-shell-gutter` wraps HUD + play + tap (not per-section gutters)
- **Coffee pickup** ‚Äî badge clears on collect; engine clears rung `coffee` flag

## v1.8.4 clip + reorg UX

- **REJECTED stamp** ‚Äî fully visible inside `card-performance` (overflow visible)
- **HUD rank stack** ‚Äî rank + milestone stacked; truncate + title tooltip on narrow phones
- **Play-area inset** ‚Äî climber clamp; horizontal padding prevents sprite/hint clip
- **Frozen badge** ‚Äî imminent reorg next rung labeled Frozen (no shuffle telegraph)

## v1.8.5 corridor + hazards

- **Center corridor** ‚Äî `.player-at-corridor`, `.rung-center--corridor` before first tap; L/R control unchanged
- **`#imminentHint`** ‚Äî next-rung panel through Intern phase (**40 rungs**); safe-side glow on imminent rung when `shouldShowImminentHint()` true
- **Obstacle badges** ‚Äî slate **Gate** (Manager+), emerald **Plant** (CEO+); same dodge rules as meetings/deadlines
- **Layout QA** ‚Äî `npm run qa:layout` after layout changes (post-tap width stable)
- **320√ó568** ‚Äî compact HUD + tap deck; rung rows scale to 32px min so seven rungs fit

## v1.9 / v2.0 UI addenda

- **Sprint HUD chip** ‚Äî Synergy Sprint wall-clock countdown
- **Revive button** ‚Äî `#reviveAdBtn` ‚ÄúMandatory HR Training‚Äù on qualifying game-over
- **Avatar picker** ‚Äî `#avatarIconBtn` on home (localStorage emoji)
- **Game-over toast** ‚Äî `.toast-above-game-over-actions` above RE-APPLY row
- **PA logo footer** ‚Äî official Prompt Anatomy logo asset in `#homeBrandFooter`
- **Sound FAB** ‚Äî visible in Telegram light theme

